A very simple ruby module to access Xen informations.

How to use it :

x=Xen::XenServer.new

puts x.has? "non-existant"
puts x.has? "domu2"
puts x.slices

s=x.get("domu2")
s2=x.get("Domain-0")

puts s.time
puts s2.time
sleep(10)
x.update
puts s.time
puts s2.time

